Interface AttributeWriteSizeAdvanced

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadSize, AttributeWriteSize
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Size
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSize, AbstractUiWidgetAbstractWindow.SizeWindowImpl, AbstractUiWidgetNative.SizeImpl, UiWidgetAdapterGwtTree.TreeNodeAdapter.SizeImpl

    public interface AttributeWriteSizeAdvanced
extends AttributeWriteSize
    This interface gives read and write access to the size of an object.

    1.0.0
    Author:
